text: Mimolaia acaiuba is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1998. It is known from Colombia.BioLib.cz - Mimolaia acaiuba. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1998
